{"tid":2043233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍玩fake news玩到台灣自由時報衝出黎澄清，華記呀叔同李力持應該呢世都去唔到台灣勒","createTime":"2020-05-30T09:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T11:19:47.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d289e227f14de9c5f951d4cd28fa42437764a3c","tid":2043233,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwirefactcheck/posts/133519811652115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwirefactcheck%2Fposts%2F133519811652115&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=45aafc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwirefactcheck/posts/133519811652115</a><br />\n<br />\n【傳真社 Fact Check】華記頻道及李力持用自由時報舊圖指台警抬走香港難民<br />\n<br />\nWKtv華記頻道Facebook專頁於5月29日轉發李力持Facebook於同日分享的一張圖片，圖片顯示4名身穿台灣警察制服的男子，將一名身穿黑色上衣的男子按在地上，圖中配以「台灣黑警抬走台北車站香港難民」。李力持Facebook同時在分享的圖片配上字句「突發：I can't breathe 。。我不能呼吸了！ 曱甴發火，廣傳手足，要私了呆灣解散呆灣警隊😯🎤」<br />\n<br />\nWKtv華記頻道Facebook專頁的轉發吸引超過500個反應、66個留言及25次分享。而李力持Facebook的圖片，吸引了超過1200個反應、81個留言及149次分享。<br />\n<br />\n台灣自由時報於同日下午1時發文澄清，表示「經過本報查證，該張在臉書上盛傳的圖片，為2018年9月25日台北捷運警察隊進行演練時的新聞照片，由本報記者羅沛德攝影。並非是網路上盛傳的「台版黑警」抬走難民等假訊息。」<br />\n<br />\n傳真社透過電郵聯絡李力持，及在WKtv華記頻道Facebook專頁的帖文留言，問會否就不實內容刪帖，暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/102396794_133519721652124_6367595359157354496_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Nd6KgIdSmA4AX8ec93k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=6026648062543191d3a1be4ea6bc2393&amp;oe=5EF700C9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F102396794_133519721652124_6367595359157354496_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DNd6KgIdSmA4AX8ec93k%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D6026648062543191d3a1be4ea6bc2393%26oe%3D5EF700C9&h=7d888736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/100922765_133519744985455_8316446609487429632_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=FtSj3LrpOd4AX_ZJXMf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=08b1bcead0109a2d536ab7e0418947ce&amp;oe=5EF9940E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F100922765_133519744985455_8316446609487429632_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DFtSj3LrpOd4AX_ZJXMf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D08b1bcead0109a2d536ab7e0418947ce%26oe%3D5EF9940E&h=4bf0d384&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f085f22fd5520d1935b883b18886efdcca2c2df","tid":2043233,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3180921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180921&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2a737859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180921&h=5194e642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3180921</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕自從去年香港反送中事件以來，香港「黑警」便爭議不斷，未料近日有香港臉書社團流傳，台北車站出現大量「台版黑警」抬走香港難民的訊息，對此，專研資訊戰的學者沈伯洋指出，此為假訊息，並且盜用本報舊圖。經過本報查證後，發現網路上流傳的圖片為2018年9月25日台北捷運警隊進行演練的新聞照片。<br />\n<br />\n沈伯洋今日凌晨在臉書上指出，臉書上有關香港的社團近日出現大量「台版黑警在台北車站抬走香港難民」的圖片，他指出這是假訊息，盜用的圖片為本報去年的照片。沈伯洋還說，這只是冰山一角，「每天都要被這些東西煩死」。<br />\n<br />\n經過本報查證，該張在臉書上盛傳的圖片，為2018年9月25日台北捷運警察隊進行演練時的新聞照片，由本報記者羅沛德攝影。並非是網路上盛傳的「台版黑警」抬走難民等假訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>網友們看到沈伯洋的貼文後，紛紛留言表示，「台灣警察換制服了，連這種功課也不做？」、「制服都換一年多了」、「這是舊制服了」、「這些香港社團有大量中國人在製造、散播偽造新聞」、「沒戴口罩」、「只好每年換制服了」。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7ac8f1161c90e25483a1b5cd9b5b048ad9087a","tid":2043233,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"舊到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f86aaaa8149b00cd5125351593a9bf57e154c3a","tid":2043233,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c7ac8f1161c90e25483a1b5cd9b5b048ad9087a","tid":2043233,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"舊到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"唔怕舊，只要觀眾受"},{"pid":"5f8619cbe85b8d7e9795811e249518261ce7b38f","tid":2043233,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca18fad710d55e2db1a1efffcf211131d8d96b4","tid":2043233,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d289e227f14de9c5f951d4cd28fa42437764a3c","tid":2043233,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwirefactcheck/posts/133519811652115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwirefactcheck%2Fposts%2F133519811652115&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD9mOP5%2FvN4